  "texts": [
    "The study aims to analyze the construction of interdisciplinary STEAM curricula and provide recommendations for improving the integration competence of teachers and expanding the professional STEAM teaching team.",
    "The study highlights several outcomes related to the interdisciplinary integration of STEAM curricula:",
    "1.The need to expand the professional team of STEAM educators and enhance their integration competence.",
    "2.The importance of strengthening the support system for STEAM curriculum integration, involving multiple stakeholders.",
    "3.The necessity of avoiding formalistic curriculum integration, with a focus on preventing the narrowing and over-generalization of themes."
  ],
